ratives, academic readings of the artist's work, anecdotes and remembrances-embracing the places where the personal, the political, and the artistic meet.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 06. Mrz 2024) 0aCardinal-Schubert, Joane,-1942-2009. 0aIndian paintingzCanada. 0aPainterszCanadavBiography. 0aPainters-Canada-Biography. 0aSiksika artzCanada. 7aART / Native American.2bisacsh1 aCardinal-Schubert, Joane, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGarneau, David, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHarnett, Tanya, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMacRae, Alisdair, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMcMaster, Gerald, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSchubert, Mike, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSharman, Lindsey V., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSharman, Lindsey, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aWestra, Monique, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertACUP Complete eBook-Package 2017z978311127365508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertACUP Upgrade eBook-Package 2017z978311127619940uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9781552389515?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781552389515423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781552389515/original  a978-3-11-127365-5  ACUP Complete eBook-Package 2017b2017  a978-3-11-127619-9  ACUP Upgrade eBook-Package 2017b2017  aGBV-deGruyter-alles